WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

01:06.540 --> 01:08.000
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:08.000 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 21]

01:16.720 --> 01:18.140
I wanted to form a cultivation partnership with Lifei,

01:18.880 --> 01:20.170
but I feared that my uncle wouldn't agree.

01:22.470 --> 01:23.620
She panicked

01:24.000 --> 01:25.220
and went straight in to ask why.

01:32.470 --> 01:34.620
Since both Lei Xiuyuan and Ji Tongzhou

01:34.640 --> 01:36.500
want to vouch for Jiang Lifei,

01:37.470 --> 01:39.700
we can test whether these three

01:40.270 --> 01:41.810
are lying.

01:43.910 --> 01:47.450
My disciple and Jiang Lifei were indeed with me.

01:50.000 --> 01:53.780
Are you going to interrogate me as well?

02:07.960 --> 02:08.500
Xiuyuan!

02:19.620 --> 02:20.620
Sir, what is this?

02:20.830 --> 02:23.340
What have I done to offend you?

02:23.960 --> 02:26.740
My eyes must have been playing tricks on me just now.

02:26.900 --> 02:28.650
Maybe I was mistaken.

02:28.710 --> 02:29.340
Everyone,

02:29.550 --> 02:30.740
we've found the culprit!

02:38.200 --> 02:38.850
Mr. Shi!

02:39.870 --> 02:40.570
Shi Chengtian,

02:40.870 --> 02:42.060
tell everyone about your dealings

02:42.080 --> 02:43.020
with the demons!

02:47.590 --> 02:48.300
You're lying!

02:48.960 --> 02:50.900
When did I ever collude with demons?

02:52.360 --> 02:53.370
This monster-bewitching powder

02:53.390 --> 02:54.370
was found on you.

02:54.800 --> 02:55.530
Still denying it?

02:55.760 --> 02:56.220
You...

02:57.040 --> 02:57.650
Impossible!

02:58.240 --> 02:59.410
I used up that powder long ago!

03:00.080 --> 03:01.130
You're framing me!

03:03.960 --> 03:05.340
This is a setup! A frame-up!

03:06.960 --> 03:07.970
Everyone.

03:08.640 --> 03:09.220
Mr. Shen.

03:09.480 --> 03:10.060
Mr. Shen.

03:10.270 --> 03:10.810
Mr. Shen.

03:11.320 --> 03:12.570
He's the one who colluded with demons.

03:12.830 --> 03:14.090
It's got nothing to do with us.

03:14.320 --> 03:15.740
We were just trying to make some money.

03:16.480 --> 03:17.020
Right, right.

03:17.040 --> 03:18.460
That person in red said

03:18.990 --> 03:20.090
that if we drove the beasts mad,

03:20.640 --> 03:21.620
we could

03:21.640 --> 03:23.460
kill them openly and sell them for money.

03:24.960 --> 03:26.180
Person in red?

03:26.480 --> 03:27.090
Yes, yes.

03:32.520 --> 03:33.130
Someone!

03:33.550 --> 03:35.340
Take Shi Chengtian and that man away!

03:35.760 --> 03:36.690
Keep them under tight watch!

03:36.960 --> 03:38.340
Wait, I...

03:39.200 --> 03:40.130
- It's got nothing to do with me.
- Shen...

03:40.590 --> 03:41.690
It's nothing to do with me!

03:42.430 --> 03:43.060
Mercy!

03:43.320 --> 03:44.900
It's got nothing to do with me!

03:45.360 --> 03:46.370
Have mercy!

03:47.920 --> 03:49.810
That person in red Shi Chengtian mentioned

03:50.080 --> 03:52.180
must be a demon Guardian.

03:53.640 --> 03:54.620
It's Rakshasa.

03:55.080 --> 03:56.900
I fought her last night.

03:58.640 --> 04:00.650
So Rakshasa is behind all this.

04:00.990 --> 04:02.340
Demons are cunning and treacherous.

04:02.360 --> 04:03.460
Hard to guard against.

04:04.270 --> 04:05.900
From now on, we need to be extra careful

04:06.390 --> 04:08.530
and watch out for demons sneaking in.

04:09.080 --> 04:10.690
Given Shi Chengtian's strength,

04:11.960 --> 04:14.970
he couldn't have helped a demon escape the city.

04:16.590 --> 04:18.090
We still need to find out

04:18.870 --> 04:20.010
who the real inside contact is.

04:21.200 --> 04:22.660
After last night's city-wide sweep,

04:22.910 --> 04:25.810
the demons wouldn't dare stay.

04:25.880 --> 04:26.940
They've probably fled by now.

04:27.520 --> 04:28.540
Facing such a massive threat,

04:28.760 --> 04:30.890
we must stand together.

04:31.200 --> 04:33.770
That was the whole point of this Shanhai Gathering.

04:34.470 --> 04:35.690
Elder Cuixuan! This is bad!

04:40.440 --> 04:41.300
Sir,

04:41.680 --> 04:43.100
Wuyue Court just sent an urgent message.

04:43.390 --> 04:45.540
A demon spy broke into Hushe Peak.

04:55.710 --> 04:56.450
Sir,

04:56.790 --> 04:59.330
does Wuyue Court have a Hushe Peak?

04:59.790 --> 05:00.420
Quiet.

05:02.000 --> 05:02.860
No more questions.

05:08.440 --> 05:09.940
All Wuyue Court disciples,

05:10.390 --> 05:13.330
return with me immediately.

05:13.760 --> 05:14.450
Sir,

05:15.560 --> 05:16.690
Jiang Lifei and Lei Xiuyuan

05:16.710 --> 05:18.100
were my friends at the academy.

05:18.470 --> 05:19.690
I'd like them to stay a few more days

05:19.830 --> 05:20.940
so I can ask how things are going there.

05:25.790 --> 05:26.450
Cuixuan.

05:31.710 --> 05:33.300
Duanming City has just settled down.

05:33.680 --> 05:36.330
We could use skilled disciples to help with defense.

05:36.440 --> 05:38.100
Do me a favor

05:38.350 --> 05:40.980
and let them stay a little longer.

05:45.560 --> 05:46.130
Fine.

05:46.640 --> 05:48.180
You two stay and help.

05:48.790 --> 05:50.370
Once Duanming City is secure,

05:50.790 --> 05:52.180
come back right away.

06:11.360 --> 06:12.640
[Duanming City Inn]

06:12.640 --> 06:14.370
Are these demons everywhere at once?

06:14.680 --> 06:16.210
Causing trouble here while ambushing us there.

06:17.320 --> 06:18.740
But Deng and I had a deal.

06:19.030 --> 06:19.770
If anything goes wrong,

06:19.790 --> 06:20.570
he'd come in right away.

06:21.030 --> 06:21.660
How is it?

06:22.150 --> 06:22.940
Not bad, right?

06:27.350 --> 06:28.570
Will they suspect something?

06:29.230 --> 06:29.980
Relax.

06:30.120 --> 06:31.130
I've cleared it with my master.

06:31.150 --> 06:32.100
He'll play along.

06:34.790 --> 06:37.770
Sorry to drag everyone into this.

06:38.320 --> 06:39.420
What are you talking about?

06:39.830 --> 06:41.420
This is something we want to do too.

06:42.440 --> 06:43.420
Gelin's right.

06:44.150 --> 06:46.330
We were born into the imperial bloodline

06:46.790 --> 06:48.300
and have been hunted by Longming Sanctuary.

06:48.710 --> 06:50.660
If it weren't for righteous people risking their lives to save us,

06:51.000 --> 06:52.300
we wouldn't be here today.

06:54.760 --> 06:55.450
Now that

06:55.470 --> 06:56.980
we're seeing such injustice,

06:57.440 --> 06:58.690
how could we stand by?

07:00.590 --> 07:02.300
We worked well together

07:02.350 --> 07:03.130
and got out clean.

07:05.960 --> 07:08.100
I always thought Mr. Zuo Qiu's talk

07:08.790 --> 07:10.100
about serving the people

07:10.200 --> 07:12.100
and purifying the world

07:12.790 --> 07:14.660
was just empty words.

07:15.520 --> 07:16.620
Now I see

07:16.960 --> 07:18.810
how hard it is to stand up to power

07:19.200 --> 07:20.860
and fight for what's right.

07:21.470 --> 07:22.890
Hard as it was, we did it.

07:23.910 --> 07:24.500
Come on!

07:24.910 --> 07:25.810
Everyone,

07:26.200 --> 07:27.300
we've triumphed.

07:27.320 --> 07:28.420
Time for a good drink.

07:28.880 --> 07:29.890
- Here. - Cheers!

07:39.440 --> 07:40.210
What a shame.

07:40.320 --> 07:40.690
Here.

07:40.710 --> 07:42.660
These sects are divided.

07:43.710 --> 07:44.980
With a little provocation from the demons,

07:45.230 --> 07:46.810
we fall apart

07:46.960 --> 07:47.690
and turn on each other.

07:48.440 --> 07:50.130
News reached my master, Sect Leader Miao.

07:50.440 --> 07:52.620
He told Changyue and me to hurry back to Dizang Sect.

07:55.790 --> 07:57.740
My uncle wants me back at Xingzheng Hall as soon as possible.

07:58.120 --> 08:00.180
The demons sent only a single Guardian,

08:00.710 --> 08:02.500
yet they threw Mountain and Sea Sects into utter chaos.

08:03.120 --> 08:04.300
We can't underestimate them.

08:04.640 --> 08:06.010
He wants me back to train

08:06.200 --> 08:07.330
so I'll be ready

08:07.350 --> 08:08.500
for the Sea Calamity.

08:10.590 --> 08:12.100
We barely had time to catch up,

08:12.470 --> 08:13.540
and now you're all leaving.

08:14.230 --> 08:15.250
Who knows

08:15.560 --> 08:16.770
when we'll see each other again?

08:20.590 --> 08:22.420
We'll cross that bridge when we get to it.

08:22.710 --> 08:23.620
Next time we meet,

08:23.640 --> 08:25.420
it'll likely be the Sea Calamity.

08:35.960 --> 08:36.810
Before that,

08:38.230 --> 08:40.420
I'd like to ask you all for a favor.

08:47.040 --> 08:50.060
Ever since I was little, I've known a girl.

08:51.710 --> 08:54.940
I think she's the most beautiful

08:55.710 --> 08:56.730
and lovely girl in the world.

08:59.920 --> 09:01.140
I've always wanted to marry her.

09:03.470 --> 09:05.300
We all know.

09:15.960 --> 09:18.210
You all are the dearest friends to Changyue and me.

09:19.200 --> 09:20.660
Before we part,

09:20.960 --> 09:22.970
I want you all to witness this.

09:24.590 --> 09:25.140
Ye,

09:25.320 --> 09:26.060
- you... - Changyue.

09:27.870 --> 09:28.780
The Sea Calamity is coming.

09:29.800 --> 09:30.780
No one knows what lies ahead.

09:32.200 --> 09:33.330
Better to cherish the one beside you

09:34.710 --> 09:35.660
than to live with regret.

09:39.200 --> 09:39.730
Changyue,

09:41.510 --> 09:42.940
will you be my wife?

09:57.440 --> 09:58.210
My head hurts.

09:59.080 --> 10:00.330
I'm going to my room to rest.

10:02.590 --> 10:03.210
Changyue.

10:07.040 --> 10:07.610
Changyue.

10:14.750 --> 10:15.610
I'll go check.

10:37.630 --> 10:38.210
Tongzhou.

10:38.750 --> 10:40.140
During the Wanxian Sect's questioning today,

10:40.180 --> 10:41.210
you were quick on your feet.

10:41.680 --> 10:43.610
You're getting almost as good at lying as I am.

10:47.460 --> 10:48.300
Actually,

10:49.590 --> 10:50.780
I wasn't entirely lying.

10:57.230 --> 10:57.850
Tongzhou,

10:58.460 --> 11:00.730
we made that three-year pact back at Lugong Town.

11:01.300 --> 11:02.140
How about we move it up?

11:04.750 --> 11:05.330
Sure.

11:05.680 --> 11:07.060
We should've done this long ago.

11:07.750 --> 11:10.020
But I won't lose.

11:11.470 --> 11:11.940
Tomorrow?

11:12.820 --> 11:13.380
At the Wu hour.

11:13.990 --> 11:14.850
Alright. Enough.

11:16.460 --> 11:17.210
Why fight?

11:18.110 --> 11:18.780
Aren't you tired?

11:19.820 --> 11:21.260
Right now, the most important thing

11:21.420 --> 11:22.780
is helping Ye Ye and Changyue

11:22.820 --> 11:24.090
with their wedding.

11:24.470 --> 11:25.450
If you really need to fight,

11:25.820 --> 11:26.660
wait until it's over

11:27.100 --> 11:28.020
and find a place to settle it.

11:29.110 --> 11:29.690
- Alright. - Fine.

11:38.420 --> 11:39.690
After Fanghu Island,

11:40.820 --> 11:41.780
I suddenly realized

11:43.100 --> 11:44.210
I can't wait any longer.

11:44.980 --> 11:45.810
Waiting any longer

11:47.180 --> 11:48.660
would only hurt you and Gelin.

11:50.460 --> 11:51.450
Time slips away

11:52.820 --> 11:53.810
in the blink of an eye.

11:55.180 --> 11:56.380
I don't want to waste any more time.

11:59.230 --> 12:00.380
I want to be with you.

12:02.980 --> 12:04.540
I want you to be my wife.

12:04.630 --> 12:05.540
- I want... - Enough, Ye!

12:06.230 --> 12:06.970
Stop.

12:07.830 --> 12:09.300
I said I needed time to think.

12:29.660 --> 12:30.210
Gelin.

12:31.590 --> 12:32.260
Changyue.

12:35.750 --> 12:37.810
You should be discussing the wedding with Ye.

12:37.830 --> 12:38.570
Why are you looking for me?

12:39.080 --> 12:39.610
Gelin.

12:39.870 --> 12:41.330
Ye and I... I...

12:41.470 --> 12:42.180
Changyue.

12:45.960 --> 12:47.140
You seem smart,

12:47.870 --> 12:49.090
but you're really clueless.

12:50.440 --> 12:51.780
I used to worry

12:51.800 --> 12:53.020
Ye wouldn't take good care of you.

12:54.750 --> 12:55.900
Turns out I worried for nothing.

12:58.200 --> 13:00.020
He takes great care of you.

13:00.750 --> 13:01.730
He's worth marrying.

13:08.230 --> 13:08.900
Gelin.

13:09.540 --> 13:10.940
I let you down.

13:11.540 --> 13:14.540
Before, I was too caught up in my own things.

13:15.040 --> 13:16.380
I thought you were still young,

13:16.590 --> 13:18.260
so I kept things from you.

13:19.200 --> 13:21.180
You ended up going all the way to the East Sea

13:21.200 --> 13:22.450
and suffering so much.

13:23.510 --> 13:24.780
It's all my fault.

13:26.440 --> 13:28.180
I'm sorry.

13:30.320 --> 13:31.020
Changyue,

13:31.660 --> 13:32.730
don't worry.

13:33.710 --> 13:35.450
I don't like Ye anymore.

13:36.510 --> 13:37.060
Really.

13:39.800 --> 13:41.660
I like someone else now.

13:42.540 --> 13:44.090
I don't even remember those childhood things.

13:47.830 --> 13:48.420
Gelin.

13:49.540 --> 13:50.780
Listen to me,

13:51.230 --> 13:53.570
liking someone isn't a crime.

13:53.590 --> 13:55.330
You didn't have to run so far away.

13:55.830 --> 13:57.140
I really don't like him anymore.

13:57.750 --> 13:59.020
You don't have to turn him down because of me.

14:01.660 --> 14:02.810
Ye was right.

14:04.040 --> 14:05.180
Time slips away

14:05.400 --> 14:06.420
in the blink of an eye.

14:08.110 --> 14:09.450
We shouldn't waste any more time.

14:11.870 --> 14:14.090
I genuinely wish you two the best.

14:16.440 --> 14:17.090
Unless...

14:18.800 --> 14:20.330
Unless, after you get married,

14:20.590 --> 14:21.850
you decide you don't want me anymore.

14:28.040 --> 14:29.780
What are you saying, silly girl?

14:30.920 --> 14:32.180
Talking nonsense.

14:34.630 --> 14:35.970
Always talking nonsense.

14:41.160 --> 14:42.540
No matter where we are

14:43.200 --> 14:44.450
or how far apart,

14:45.230 --> 14:46.690
I'll always miss you.

14:47.350 --> 14:50.180
And I believe you'll miss me too.

14:51.630 --> 14:52.810
We'll always be sisters,

14:53.400 --> 14:55.540
through life and death.

15:34.110 --> 15:34.690
Gelin.

15:35.710 --> 15:36.330
What's wrong?

15:39.680 --> 15:41.490
Lifei said you went to Yingcui Island.

15:41.990 --> 15:44.090
I thought I'd never see you again.

15:49.590 --> 15:50.940
I thought you were all leaving

15:50.960 --> 15:52.180
and never coming back.

15:53.470 --> 15:54.300
I didn't want you...

15:56.400 --> 15:57.300
you all to worry.

16:04.440 --> 16:05.300
You're hurt?

16:14.710 --> 16:15.380
Feeling better?

16:27.870 --> 16:28.810
Treasure it that much?

16:31.510 --> 16:34.970
Did some special girl give it to you?

16:37.110 --> 16:38.850
It's the crest of the Jiufeng Clan.

16:48.440 --> 16:49.570
Why no eyes?

16:50.510 --> 16:51.450
Did you lose them?

16:55.750 --> 16:56.780
You want to see the eyes?

16:57.990 --> 16:58.690
Yeah.

16:59.200 --> 17:00.570
It would look better

17:00.710 --> 17:01.690
with eyes.

17:37.600 --> 17:38.580
This is...?

17:56.990 --> 17:57.730
Now it has one.

18:06.340 --> 18:07.340
What did you do?

18:14.340 --> 18:16.050
I swear by the Jiufeng Clan,

18:16.990 --> 18:18.730
I will never betray Baili Gelin.

18:22.840 --> 18:23.690
Through life and death,

18:24.400 --> 18:25.180
we'll never part.

18:28.960 --> 18:29.940
Lu,

18:30.640 --> 18:31.730
are you crazy?

18:36.470 --> 18:37.900
Take it off for me.

18:39.070 --> 18:40.490
Once it's on, it can never be removed.

18:41.750 --> 18:42.490
Baili Gelin,

18:43.440 --> 18:44.730
you started this.

19:14.550 --> 19:15.210
Come out.

19:19.310 --> 19:20.380
My Lord,

19:21.440 --> 19:24.340
have you finally seen their true colors now?

19:25.640 --> 19:26.730
Stop using the demon clan.

19:27.960 --> 19:28.900
Their situation

19:29.840 --> 19:31.180
is no different from yours 500 years ago.

19:32.510 --> 19:33.770
My Lord, you remember me now?

19:34.840 --> 19:36.210
Your soul has been hiding in a bone-devouring butterfly.

19:37.230 --> 19:38.250
You've waited centuries

19:39.160 --> 19:40.450
for a result, haven't you?

19:41.470 --> 19:42.210
The Sea Calamity is coming.

19:43.200 --> 19:44.210
Instead of mutual destruction,

19:44.960 --> 19:45.970
it's better to go home while you can.

19:47.680 --> 19:48.490
My Lord!

19:57.710 --> 19:58.380
Xiuyuan,

19:58.510 --> 19:59.340
thank you

19:59.340 --> 20:00.340
for helping with the wedding.

20:02.440 --> 20:03.210
I only hope that one day,

20:04.100 --> 20:05.900
you can step out of being a stand-in.

20:06.440 --> 20:07.620
But I still have a mission to fulfill.

20:08.470 --> 20:09.970
Until it's done,

20:10.840 --> 20:11.940
I can't afford a single wrong step.

20:13.640 --> 20:14.450
Mission?

20:15.160 --> 20:17.010
The true king of Gaolu

20:17.750 --> 20:18.490
isn't named Ye,

20:19.160 --> 20:19.860
but

20:21.310 --> 20:22.010
Yecha.

20:25.470 --> 20:26.420
That Demon Lord?

20:27.030 --> 20:27.970
In ancient times,

20:28.790 --> 20:30.210
when Yecha was still a Divine Lord,

20:30.840 --> 20:32.970
our ancestors followed him.

20:33.510 --> 20:34.420
A thousand years ago,

20:34.600 --> 20:35.450
heaven's wrath descended.

20:35.960 --> 20:38.860
The Ye clan was ordered to guard the Central Plains.

20:39.160 --> 20:40.210
Our duty is to find the Divine Lord

20:40.310 --> 20:41.660
and end heaven's wrath.

20:42.070 --> 20:43.290
That is our mission.

20:43.790 --> 20:44.530
So

20:45.270 --> 20:46.770
until it's fulfilled,

20:48.160 --> 20:49.180
I don't even dare to die.

20:50.100 --> 20:50.820
Is the mission

20:53.230 --> 20:54.340
really that important?

20:54.960 --> 20:55.860
A true promise is etched in stone.

20:56.310 --> 20:57.380
It can't be broken lightly.

20:58.270 --> 20:59.660
Not in a thousand years,

21:00.440 --> 21:01.380
not in ten thousand.

21:04.440 --> 21:04.940
Oh,

21:05.310 --> 21:06.380
I saw

21:06.400 --> 21:08.180
you and Lifei made up again.

21:08.600 --> 21:09.050
So,

21:09.340 --> 21:11.100
are you two in love?

21:12.070 --> 21:12.620
I do like her.

21:14.160 --> 21:15.420
But I don't know how she feels.

21:16.680 --> 21:18.530
Lifei seems happy enough.

21:18.960 --> 21:19.730
It's probably mutual.

21:26.030 --> 21:26.690
Uncle.

21:28.680 --> 21:30.450
I'd like to stay for Ye Ye's wedding

21:30.990 --> 21:31.900
before returning to Xingzheng Hall.

21:32.310 --> 21:37.380
Our highest techniques require cutting off attachments and desires.

21:39.270 --> 21:42.100
If you don't focus on your training,

21:42.790 --> 21:44.380
how will you help your brother

21:44.750 --> 21:45.820
secure the kingdom

21:45.840 --> 21:46.970
and achieve greatness?

21:47.550 --> 21:48.290
Do I have to give up

21:48.310 --> 21:49.730
the one I love to achieve greatness?

21:50.160 --> 21:51.420
Remember who you are.

21:52.200 --> 21:53.290
Can't a prince of the Yue State

21:53.310 --> 21:54.420
pursue the one he loves?

21:54.790 --> 21:56.690
To protect this kingdom,

21:56.880 --> 21:58.580
you must master the Xuanhua Sacred Fire

21:58.640 --> 21:59.620
and attain immortality!

21:59.920 --> 22:01.140
I don't need the Xuanhua Sacred Fire

22:01.200 --> 22:01.940
or immortality

22:02.230 --> 22:03.250
to protect the Yue State!

22:04.070 --> 22:06.100
Jiang Lifei's heart already belongs to another.

22:06.440 --> 22:07.940
Can't you see that?

22:10.990 --> 22:12.290
Lifei has feelings for me.

22:14.400 --> 22:16.770
At worst, I'll give up my title as Prince

22:17.030 --> 22:18.050
and abandon my path to immortality!

22:18.640 --> 22:19.140
You!

22:19.640 --> 22:20.180
You...

22:36.510 --> 22:37.140
Changyue,

22:37.750 --> 22:40.290
no bride in the world is more beautiful than you.

22:41.400 --> 22:43.290
It's just this dress that's beautiful.

22:44.030 --> 22:45.290
Jiao prepared it.

22:46.470 --> 22:47.730
She said

22:48.310 --> 22:50.490
she'd give Lifei one when she gets married.

23:35.840 --> 23:36.900
So beautiful.

23:49.160 --> 23:50.380
From the primal chaos,

23:50.600 --> 23:51.770
yin and yang were formed.

23:52.640 --> 23:53.970
Love between mortals

23:54.070 --> 23:55.530
is passed down through rites and teachings.

23:56.270 --> 23:57.580
Today, bound by ritual,

23:57.790 --> 23:58.970
they wed before these guests.

23:59.840 --> 24:01.100
They share the ritual feast

24:01.100 --> 24:02.380
and drink the nuptial wine.

24:02.710 --> 24:03.770
With heaven and earth as witness,

24:04.160 --> 24:05.690
under the sun and the moon.

24:07.200 --> 24:08.730
First bow to heaven and earth.

24:13.990 --> 24:14.660
Tongzhou!

24:15.270 --> 24:15.900
Tongzhou.

24:17.750 --> 24:18.380
Lanya?

24:19.750 --> 24:20.380
Lanya.

24:20.550 --> 24:21.180
Tongzhou.

24:23.070 --> 24:23.690
Lanya,

24:24.400 --> 24:25.250
what happened?

24:25.600 --> 24:26.290
Tongzhou.

24:26.680 --> 24:27.860
Wugou invaded the Yue State!

24:28.100 --> 24:29.140
Duantu has fallen!

24:32.200 --> 24:33.100
- What? - What?

24:37.840 --> 24:38.660
Tonghe...

24:39.160 --> 24:40.970
Tonghe was captured by Zong Quan!

24:41.880 --> 24:42.620
What?

24:45.230 --> 24:46.180
It was Zhijie.

24:46.990 --> 24:48.730
He held off Longming Sanctuary

24:49.160 --> 24:50.450
so I could escape.

24:51.160 --> 24:52.250
We're going back to Duantu right now!

24:52.840 --> 24:53.490
Don't act rashly.

24:54.920 --> 24:56.340
Since Zong Quan showed up,

24:56.790 --> 24:59.250
Longming Sanctuary must have fully mobilized.

25:00.840 --> 25:02.450
Let's return to Xingzheng Hall, gather the disciples,

25:02.880 --> 25:04.100
and go rescue him together.

25:04.840 --> 25:05.530
Tongzhou!

25:12.600 --> 25:13.450
Are you ready?

25:18.750 --> 25:20.050
If you are, let's move.

25:20.230 --> 25:21.340
The three of us will go to Duantu with you.

25:21.880 --> 25:23.290
Ye Ye and Changyue are going back to Dizang Sect first,

25:23.470 --> 25:24.530
then they'll meet up with us.

25:25.230 --> 25:25.690
Right.

25:26.200 --> 25:27.730
Longming Sanctuary is acting against all reason.

25:28.230 --> 25:29.730
We'll report to our sect leader

25:30.070 --> 25:31.050
and join forces with other sects

25:31.070 --> 25:32.290
to stop them.

25:32.880 --> 25:33.620
The situation is unclear.

25:34.270 --> 25:35.290
You'll all be dragged into this.

25:35.990 --> 25:36.860
If we can't

25:37.440 --> 25:38.770
watch out for each other in times like these,

25:39.070 --> 25:40.620
what's the point of cultivation?

25:41.920 --> 25:42.660
- Right. - Yes.

26:10.440 --> 26:11.380
How could this happen?

26:26.070 --> 26:26.690
Mo Chen.

26:41.710 --> 26:42.290
Chen!

26:42.960 --> 26:43.530
Chen.

26:44.100 --> 26:44.690
Chen.

26:45.550 --> 26:46.290
Tongzhou.

26:46.750 --> 26:48.420
It was Longming Sanctuary.

26:50.400 --> 26:51.900
It was Zong Quan.

27:17.070 --> 27:18.250
Move! Behave!

27:18.270 --> 27:19.250
- Go! - Keep up!

27:19.680 --> 27:20.420
Hurry!

27:20.420 --> 27:21.420
[Xingzheng Hall]

27:23.340 --> 27:27.210
You must avenge

27:28.710 --> 27:29.730
us.

27:30.030 --> 27:30.690
Chen.

27:31.230 --> 27:31.860
Chen!

27:33.470 --> 27:34.140
Chen!

28:06.790 --> 28:08.180
No survivors.

28:09.270 --> 28:10.660
It's been less than two years

28:10.680 --> 28:11.730
since we heavily wounded Zong Quan.

28:12.310 --> 28:14.210
How did his cultivation recover so fast?

28:14.920 --> 28:16.530
Not just recovered.

28:18.030 --> 28:19.420
He seems even stronger.

28:29.400 --> 28:30.530
He wiped out

28:31.510 --> 28:33.250
the entire Xingzheng Hall in a single night.

28:34.750 --> 28:36.530
What kind of evil art has he been practicing?

28:40.440 --> 28:41.860
Is it the Spirit-Devouring Canon?

28:44.550 --> 28:45.820
After Gaolu fell,

28:46.400 --> 28:47.450
Longming Sanctuary used every means

28:47.680 --> 28:48.620
to hunt down the imperial bloodline.

28:50.200 --> 28:51.620
They'll use the same tricks again.

28:57.800 --> 29:00.360
[Yue State Imperial Palace]

29:04.470 --> 29:05.100
Tonghe.

29:05.360 --> 29:06.180
Are you alright?

29:30.680 --> 29:31.290
Tonghe.

29:31.880 --> 29:32.250
No.

29:33.200 --> 29:33.660
No.

29:36.400 --> 29:36.970
Tonghe!

29:38.270 --> 29:38.770
No.

29:39.640 --> 29:40.420
Don't leave me.

29:47.070 --> 29:49.380
Tonghe. Tonghe!

29:51.790 --> 29:52.420
Tonghe.

29:53.680 --> 29:54.340
No!

30:02.030 --> 30:04.730
What a touching display of brotherly love.

30:10.680 --> 30:14.450
Prince Ying conspired with Xingzheng Hall to usurp the throne.

30:14.960 --> 30:16.010
The Emperor of Yue is dead.

30:16.710 --> 30:19.770
How do you like my gift?

30:20.360 --> 30:21.660
Zong Quan.

30:23.200 --> 30:24.620
I'll kill you!

30:32.270 --> 30:34.180
Xuanhua Sacred Fire?

30:42.600 --> 30:43.450
What a pity.

30:43.640 --> 30:44.900
You haven't even mastered it.

30:45.600 --> 30:47.140
You've only reached the second level.

30:47.230 --> 30:48.010
Otherwise,

30:48.200 --> 30:50.100
you might have traded a few strikes with me.

30:50.710 --> 30:52.010
You practice evil arts?

30:59.600 --> 31:00.820
The law of this world is simple.

31:01.200 --> 31:02.290
The strong rule.

31:02.750 --> 31:04.770
As long as you have the power to control everything,

31:05.070 --> 31:07.050
the means don't matter!

31:07.360 --> 31:07.900
But

31:09.200 --> 31:11.690
I don't want to kill you yet.

31:16.230 --> 31:17.820
Your spirit power is pure,

31:18.200 --> 31:19.340
and your constitution is excellent.

31:20.120 --> 31:22.210
You'll be useful to me.

31:33.990 --> 31:34.660
Tongzhou.

31:36.310 --> 31:37.450
Get Tongzhou out of here!

31:38.030 --> 31:38.620
Let's go.

31:57.710 --> 31:58.690
Zhao Zhijie, are you insane?

31:59.960 --> 32:00.620
Zhao Zhijie?

32:11.200 --> 32:12.100
They've all been controlled.

32:36.440 --> 32:38.290
Xuanhua Sacred Fire.

32:39.470 --> 32:40.820
Demon Annihilation!

33:02.470 --> 33:03.100
Lanya?

33:15.200 --> 33:15.820
Mr. Xuanshan!

33:16.470 --> 33:17.100
Tongzhou!

33:17.880 --> 33:18.380
Mr. Xuanshan.

33:18.840 --> 33:19.380
Mr. Xuanshan.

33:19.640 --> 33:20.250
Are you alright?

33:54.440 --> 33:55.010
Mr. Xuanshan.

33:55.550 --> 33:56.580
Mr. Xuanshan. Mr. Xuanshan!

33:56.990 --> 33:58.180
Mr. Xuanshan, hang in there.

33:58.310 --> 33:58.900
Mr. Xuanshan.

33:59.400 --> 33:59.970
Remember,

34:01.070 --> 34:04.620
this is the fourth level of the Xuanhua Sacred Fire.

34:05.790 --> 34:07.100
Incineration!

34:07.120 --> 34:07.770
Mr. Xuanshan.

34:08.160 --> 34:09.340
Mr. Xuanshan!

34:12.710 --> 34:14.880
[Duantu City]

34:23.800 --> 34:24.450
Let me go.

34:25.030 --> 34:25.570
Let go!

34:25.960 --> 34:27.380
A Xingzheng Hall disciple!

34:27.510 --> 34:28.090
Perfect.

34:28.320 --> 34:30.010
Xu will reward us well.

34:30.470 --> 34:32.700
Hold him tight. Don't let him move.

35:09.860 --> 35:10.490
Lu.

35:17.110 --> 35:18.650
What's this thing for?

35:19.240 --> 35:20.570
It's Longming Sanctuary's puppet seal.

35:21.420 --> 35:21.820
Well...

35:22.460 --> 35:22.820
Pup...

35:22.940 --> 35:23.780
Can it be removed?

35:24.670 --> 35:26.220
Yes, by pulling the puppet spider out.

35:26.860 --> 35:27.450
But

35:28.300 --> 35:29.340
one wrong move

35:29.670 --> 35:30.650
and it will backfire,

35:31.460 --> 35:32.220
snapping the host's neck.

35:38.590 --> 35:39.170
Mingli,

35:39.510 --> 35:41.130
after you got hurt on Fanghu Island,

35:41.150 --> 35:42.610
didn't you go back to Xingzheng Hall early?

35:42.780 --> 35:44.170
How did they catch you in Duantu?

35:44.670 --> 35:46.300
When I returned from the East Sea,

35:47.340 --> 35:49.260
I found Longming Sanctuary had ambushed Xingzheng Hall.

35:53.780 --> 35:54.420
Behave!

35:54.550 --> 35:55.860
Move it! Hurry!

35:55.900 --> 35:57.700
- Move! - Hurry!

35:57.720 --> 35:59.010
I went to find my brother for help,

35:59.470 --> 36:00.490
but his house was empty.

36:00.990 --> 36:02.220
When I went to the Commandery Princess's Manor for news,

36:02.820 --> 36:03.940
I ran right into Longming Sanctuary's people.

36:05.300 --> 36:06.970
Now their spies are everywhere.

36:07.510 --> 36:08.420
Still have no word from my brother.

36:10.070 --> 36:10.820
What about Prince Ying?

36:11.550 --> 36:12.450
Is he with you?

36:31.720 --> 36:32.260
Uncle.

36:32.980 --> 36:33.530
Uncle.

36:36.030 --> 36:36.650
Uncle.

36:58.460 --> 36:59.300
He'll pull through.

37:08.440 --> 37:09.220
Uncle

37:09.720 --> 37:10.490
Tongzhou,

37:11.300 --> 37:13.820
I pushed you into the fire today.

37:14.470 --> 37:16.970
Will you hold it against me someday?

37:19.340 --> 37:20.090
No.

37:21.300 --> 37:21.820
Uncle.

37:23.030 --> 37:24.300
I won't defy you anymore.

37:25.550 --> 37:26.490
I'll listen to you.

37:27.470 --> 37:28.490
I'll cut off attachments

37:29.340 --> 37:30.300
and master the Sacred Fire.

37:32.030 --> 37:32.610
Uncle.

37:33.780 --> 37:34.700
Don't leave me.

37:35.420 --> 37:35.940
Uncle.

37:36.510 --> 37:37.780
You must live.

37:39.150 --> 37:42.740
Live on for all eternity, in the name of the Yue State.

37:44.670 --> 37:45.260
Uncle.

37:46.510 --> 37:47.130
Uncle.

37:48.720 --> 37:49.450
Uncle!

38:00.110 --> 38:02.450
If you ever feel wronged or unhappy out there,

38:02.900 --> 38:04.050
come back to me.

38:04.550 --> 38:05.820
Forget cultivation if it comes to that.

38:05.980 --> 38:07.010
I'll support you.

38:09.460 --> 38:10.170
Got it.

38:10.940 --> 38:11.490
I'm going.

38:28.780 --> 38:29.340
Tonghe.

38:30.550 --> 38:31.130
Tonghe.

38:35.670 --> 38:36.260
Tonghe.

38:40.110 --> 38:40.700
Tonghe.

38:54.990 --> 38:55.570
Tonghe!

38:58.030 --> 38:58.570
Tonghe.

38:58.990 --> 38:59.610
Tonghe.

39:00.190 --> 39:00.820
Tonghe?

39:01.420 --> 39:02.010
Tonghe!

39:08.110 --> 39:08.860
Tongzhou.

39:10.150 --> 39:13.050
The Yue State and Jingwu

39:18.550 --> 39:19.820
are yours now.

39:20.420 --> 39:21.450
No, Tonghe.

39:22.340 --> 39:22.780
No.

39:23.030 --> 39:23.570
Tonghe.

39:23.780 --> 39:24.380
Tonghe.

39:25.590 --> 39:26.090
No!

39:27.030 --> 39:27.780
Tonghe!

39:30.340 --> 39:31.090
Tongzhou.

39:32.150 --> 39:32.820
Lifei?

39:33.510 --> 39:34.130
Lifei!

39:35.340 --> 39:35.970
Lifei.

39:36.550 --> 39:37.220
Lifei.

39:37.590 --> 39:38.450
Don't be scared.

39:38.590 --> 39:39.420
Be careful.

39:39.990 --> 39:41.650
You're still hurt. Don't get too worked up.

39:47.940 --> 39:49.780
You've been unconscious for five days.

39:50.110 --> 39:51.220
We were all so worried.

39:51.990 --> 39:52.860
Five days?

40:12.150 --> 40:12.970
All this time,

40:14.030 --> 40:15.610
you've been channeling your own spirit power

40:16.590 --> 40:17.450
into me?

40:21.300 --> 40:22.490
It was Gelin and Xiuyuan.

40:23.470 --> 40:24.900
They've been working day and night,

40:24.940 --> 40:26.220
setting up formations to repair your spirit meridians.

40:28.030 --> 40:29.220
Everything happened so fast.

40:30.510 --> 40:31.940
So much at once.

40:32.670 --> 40:33.860
I couldn't even bring myself to come see you.

40:35.820 --> 40:36.490
Scared?

40:39.670 --> 40:41.010
When we first escaped,

40:41.240 --> 40:43.340
your meridians were shattered. You were barely clinging to life.

40:44.590 --> 40:46.970
Thankfully, Xiuyuan kept us all grounded.

40:48.190 --> 40:49.300
Since the Shanhai Gathering,

40:49.510 --> 40:51.340
seeing so many people and spirits die,

40:51.990 --> 40:53.170
I suddenly realized

40:54.550 --> 40:57.780
even the strongest lives are so fragile.

40:59.030 --> 41:00.490
I was afraid we couldn't save you.

41:00.820 --> 41:02.610
Afraid you'd give up and follow your family.

41:03.860 --> 41:04.420
So,

41:06.380 --> 41:07.530
I hid outside for days,

41:07.550 --> 41:08.740
too scared to come in.

41:09.820 --> 41:10.740
Until Xiuyuan said

41:11.110 --> 41:12.050
you'd live.

41:23.980 --> 41:25.220
What does it matter if I die?

41:28.240 --> 41:30.490
I'd rather it had been me.

41:32.460 --> 41:33.650
I'm so useless.

41:34.720 --> 41:36.090
I couldn't protect anyone.

41:39.670 --> 41:41.610
Why wasn't it me?

41:43.820 --> 41:45.650
Why am I the only one left?

41:47.470 --> 41:49.050
Why only me?

41:49.900 --> 41:51.740
Because there is someone who need you.

42:03.980 --> 42:04.650
Xiuyuan.

42:15.110 --> 42:15.650
Tongzhou.

42:17.110 --> 42:18.300
You don't have time to grieve.

42:19.070 --> 42:20.260
Your brother was a great emperor.

42:21.340 --> 42:22.340
Before Duantu fell,

42:23.340 --> 42:25.380
he managed to evacuate most of the people.

42:26.190 --> 42:27.650
But many soldiers were captured

42:28.420 --> 42:29.170
and will be slaughtered.

42:30.150 --> 42:31.220
They are your people.

42:32.190 --> 42:33.170
You have to shoulder the responsibility.

42:35.860 --> 42:36.780
You don't have the right to give up.

42:37.820 --> 42:38.740
And you can't throw your life away.

42:42.050 --> 42:42.780
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:42.780 --> 42:44.560
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

42:55.800 --> 42:59.480
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

42:59.800 --> 43:02.480
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

43:02.560 --> 43:05.800
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

43:05.800 --> 43:09.080
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

43:09.200 --> 43:13.080
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

43:13.360 --> 43:16.560
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

43:16.720 --> 43:22.800
♪No calamity can rival the lingering thread of a fragrance♪

43:23.080 --> 43:27.200
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

43:27.480 --> 43:30.160
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

43:30.360 --> 43:32.280
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

43:32.400 --> 43:36.720
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

43:36.880 --> 43:40.720
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

43:41.080 --> 43:44.080
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

43:44.160 --> 43:50.280
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

43:50.480 --> 43:54.200
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

44:07.440 --> 44:11.200
♪I trade the highest heaven and endless clouds♪

44:11.400 --> 44:14.200
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

44:14.280 --> 44:17.680
♪Pierced by countless arrows, pain and illness pile on♪

44:17.680 --> 44:21.000
♪Yet I remain silent♪

44:21.160 --> 44:25.000
♪Deep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream♪

44:25.160 --> 44:28.360
♪In the distant night, bitterness blooms♪

44:28.600 --> 44:34.440
♪The grand chapter is rewritten, startling the whole world♪

44:35.000 --> 44:38.920
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

44:39.200 --> 44:41.960
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

44:42.160 --> 44:44.000
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

44:44.160 --> 44:48.360
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

44:48.600 --> 44:52.480
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

44:52.720 --> 44:55.760
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

44:55.960 --> 45:02.680
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

45:02.720 --> 45:06.680
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

45:06.920 --> 45:09.680
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

45:09.800 --> 45:11.720
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds♪

45:11.880 --> 45:16.160
♪Break through the waves; the heart's ocean knows no shore♪

45:16.360 --> 45:20.200
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

45:20.440 --> 45:23.560
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

45:23.600 --> 45:29.600
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water and falling petals♪

45:30.000 --> 45:34.360
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪
